Package js.dom

Opaque classes and interfaces simulating client-side DOM.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
DocumentRange An opaque interface from DocumentRange interface of DOM Level2 Range.
DOM An opaque interface for DOM implementors.
DOM2Core An opaque interface for DOM Level 2 Core implementors.
DOM2CSS An opaque interface for DOM Level 2 CSS implementors.
DOM2Event An opaque interface for DOM Level 2 Event implementors.
DOM2HTML An opaque interface for DOM Level 2 HTML implementors.
DOM2Range An opaque interface for DOM Level 2 Range implementors.
EventTarget An opaque interface from EventTarget interface of DOM Level2 Event.

Package js.dom Description

Opaque classes and interfaces simulating client-side DOM.

Please refer to DOM Standars for the detail description about the Document Object Model (DOM).
